<data>
    <story>
        <!-- 
            A young girl is inside the ИНТЕРКОСМОС (INTERKOSMOS), a machine that once helped astronauts get to the Moon nearly half a century ago. 
            By adjusting the gravity settings, she's able to train for longer periods while reducing the damage and tear done to her joints. 
            Valkyrie Durandal begins a new day of training.
    
            Rita comes to tell Durandal breakfast is ready. Today's dessert is Mille-feuille, known as the Napoleon. 
            Durandal is startled Rita called her using her real name, Bianka. Today, February 29th, is a special day worth commemorating, hence the name and the cake. 
            It's been 4 years since that fateful day when she met her and them. It's been so long she even has gotten used to be called "Durandal". 
            Soon Bishop Otto will put in motion his plan, and eventually they'll be able to make good on the promise they made. 
            Fulfilling that promise is the top priority of the girl known as Bianka. 
	    -->
        <scene id="0" background="dashboard.jpg">
            <bgm src="morning.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text>It's 5 in the morning.</text>
            <text>Inside a large device, a girl fastens her seat belt and turns on the power.</text>
            <text>Above the power button is a badge: a string of Russian letters surrounding a rocket.</text>
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text>И...Н...Т...Е...Р...К...О...С...М...О...С...</text>
            <text>ИНТЕРКОСМОС (INTERKOSMOS)</text>
            <text>Nearly half a century ago, with the help of Schicksal, humans had successfully sent several astronauts from different countries to the Moon.</text>
            <text>This machine is part of the legacy of that glorious era.</text>
            <speak chara="_mechanicalSound">Warm up complete.</speak>
            <speak chara="_mechanicalSound">Current analog magnification，0.2.</speak>
            <speak chara="_mechanicalSound">Starting operation.</speak>
            <text>伴随着古老机械那透着机油气味的噪音，从少女的腰部向下，空气增压系统开始为她平衡地球的重力。</text>
            <text>现在，她的脚踝和膝盖只需要承受20%的体重负荷——</text>
            <text>This way, the girl is able to run for dozens of kilometres without risking damaging and tear done to her joints.</text>
            <text>The sun rises early.</text>
            <text>Valkyrie Durandal begins a new day of training.</text>
            <goto goto="10" clockwise="1"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="10" background="gymnasium.jpg">
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="biankaSportSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">平均心率125……很好，锻炼效果不错。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="ritaMaidSmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">那么【比安卡】大人，您的早餐可以端上来了吗？</speak>
            <show chara="ritaMaidSquintClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita" remark="next">今天的甜点，是新鲜出炉的乳酪拿破仑哦。</speak>
            <remark post="U2FsdGVkX18du3l7nMcHK1ORJgIy">
                <p class="article-text-h">Note：</p>
                <p class="article-text">法式千层酥（mille-feuille）是由三层酥皮夹两层奶油或果酱制成的一类蛋糕，其发明灵感可能源自那不勒斯的披萨。</p>
                <p class="article-text">由于“Napolitain”（“那不勒斯”的形容词形式）与"Napoleon"（“拿破仑”）的拼写近似，在英文中此甜点遂被戏称为"Napoleon"；中文亦随之译作“拿破仑蛋糕”。</p>
                <p class="article-text">p.s. 由于1812年俄法战争的关系，“拿破仑”在俄罗斯是最受欢迎的蛋糕款式之一。</p>
            </remark>
            <show chara="ritaMaidSquintClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSportSurprisedClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">咦？丽塔？今天怎么突然想起做这种高热——</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">——等等。</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">刚才，你叫我……“比安卡”？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportSurprisedClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="ritaMaidNaughtyClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">诶嘿嘿。没错哦。</speak>
            <show chara="ritaMaidSquintClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">因为今天是一个值得用蛋糕纪念的特别日子嘛。</speak>
            <show chara="ritaMaidSquintClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSportSurprisedClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">今天？2月28……不对，29？</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">啊。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportHesitateClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">……</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">已经四年了吗。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">认识你也好……认识他们也好。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportHesitateClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">……连我自己都已经习惯于“幽兰黛尔”这个名字了。</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">……</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSportHesitateClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="ritaMaidNormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">主教大人会择机实施他的计划。</speak>
            <speak chara="_Rita">而我们，也终将有机会兑现自己的承诺。</speak>
            <show chara="ritaMaidNormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSportSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">……当然。</speak>
            <speak chara="_Durandal">那可是少女比安卡的头等大事。</speak>
            <goto goto="20" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="20" background="libraryDay.jpg">
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>In the valkyrie archives of Schicksal, a stack of now yellowed paper lay quietly.</text> <!-- zklm -->
            <text>This declassified document begins with——</text> <!-- zklm -->
            <text>Top Secret Mission："LONELY PANTHALASSA" </text>
            <text>Start Time: February 29th 2012</text>
            <text>Location: ██████████ - The Quantum Sea  </text>
            <text>Target: ██████████</text>
            <!-- RENAME: Members: Bianka "Durandal" Atagina (12), Rita Rossweisse (16) -->
            <text>Members: Bianka "Durandal" Ataegina (12), Rita Rossweisse (16)</text> 
            <text>Status: Closed</text>
            <text>Reviewed by: Otto Apocalypse</text>
            <goto goto="30" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="30" background="black">
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>Yes.</text>
            <text>This story will now go back in time 1461 days before February 29th 2016——</text>
            <!-- RENAME: to the moment when Bianka Atagina and Rita Rossweisse arrived at the Quantum Sea. -->
            <text>to the moment when Bianka Ataegina and Rita Rossweisse arrived at the Quantum Sea.</text>
            <goto goto="40" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="40" background="fishingVillage.jpg">
            <bgm src="bigTask.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">Gosh, these refugees are nothing but cowards!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">They're all the same no matter the era they came from!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">Can you believe they would prefer to live in hunger rather than help us sail to the sea!?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">How spineless can someone be!?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17HesitateClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">Well, before they drifted here they didn't have any sailing experience...</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">...It's natural they would be afraid of the mythical sea monster 「Leviathan」.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">What—— Are you saying it's okay for them to never leave this island? It's okay for them to keep living only picking up shells and catching crabs?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">There is a saying that goes 「The boat should be near the coast」.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_BiankaNoName">...What?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">Bianka-sama, the 「average person」 is pessimistic and realistic. Before they even start considering the rewards of their success, they look at the consequences of their failure.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17HesitateClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">If a person like that is put against the sea, a completely unknown world to them—— They won't be able to fight back against their fears.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17HesitateClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">The name 「Leviathan」...</speak>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">Makes them subconsciously believe that sailing to the sea is equal to becoming an enemy of nature itself——</speak>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">——In other words, they are committing suicide.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_RitaNoName">Thus, from their perspective, we are naive 「crazy adventurers」.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSighClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Hm. Sympathizing with the weak?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Also——</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">——Rita, how many times have I told you today?</speak>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Stop adding 「-sama」 to my name... It's creepy.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">I'm a Valkyrie who only met you right before this mission started, and you only became my adjutant due to a certain someone's insistence.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">——Please stop talking to me the same way you talk to the Bishop!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">Understood, Bianka-sama.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">.....</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <bgm src="legion.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Excuse me.</speak>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">You two... are you perhaps new here?</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaConfidentClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">...Yes.</speak>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">We've been here for 38 minutes and 25 seconds—— No, 26 seconds now.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaProudClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">However, unlike you all, we've come here to 「explore」 rather than to 「escape」.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Needless to say, until our mission is completed—— We plan to involve ourselves in all your joys and sorrows.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaConfidentClose" position="left"/>
            <!-- RENAME: I am Bianka Atagina, and this my adjutant, Rita Rossweisse—— How can we help you? -->
            <speak chara="_Bianka">I am Bianka Ataegina, and this my adjutant, Rita Rossweisse—— How can we help you?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaConfidentClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Hahahaha!</speak>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Ahahahaha!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">...What's so funny?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <!-- TYPO: My apologies! Us the elderly just like to laugh. Please don't mind it, miss explorer. -->
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">My apologies! We the elderly just like to laugh. Please don't mind it, miss explorer.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">.....</speak>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Anyway——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">I heard you two are trying to gather forces to defeat the 「Leviathan」 and open the way to the ocean.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Yes, that's correct.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Not a single person wanted to fight together with us though!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Haha... Understandable. None of them are warriors——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">——They can't be compared with heroes who have seen hell itself.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">How do you know that...</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">Hahaha, when you get to my age you can just tell by looking at someone's eyes!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_MiguelNoName">I'm Miguel. Let me get straight to the point——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Brave warriors... Would you embark on an epic hunt together with this old sailor who can't even move his left hand?</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">What?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaProudClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">You mean...</speak>
            <show chara="biankaProudClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">In short, I'll provide you with a ship and take care of steering it.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——Though all I have is a reed boat! Hahaha!</speak>
            <goto goto="50" clockwise="1"/>
        </scene>

        <!-- 
			The Leviathan has made its nest somewhere nearby, making it very hard for the people of the island to go fishing. 
			They're so afraid they haven't been able to group together and build a ship big enough to deal with it. 
			It may be strong, but there is nothing humans can't overcome. 
			After all a few hundred soldiers were able to win against 100.000 enemies in the Spanish Conquest of Peru. 
			Miguel is from Spain, before he came to this world by accident he was not only a veteran soldier who fought in the Battle of Lepanto, but also a cultured person who published several books. 
			He's not sure if they are still popular 400 years later, but some of his books were "La Galatea", "The Travails of Persiles and Sigismunda" and "Don Quixote of La Mancha". 
			He's Miguel de Cervantes Saavedra, the greatest Spanish writer in the world and one of the most important figures in the history of literature. 
		-->
        <scene id="50" background="beachIslandNoName.jpg">
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">哦，大海，我的老朋友！</speak>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">多谢你高抬贵手，让我这条发了霉的老破船，到今天也没有散架！</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSighClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">……怎么了，突然诗兴大发的样子。</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSighClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">哈哈哈……看啊，这条芦苇船吃了三年的灰，竟然还这么结实！</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">……“利维坦”已经围困岛屿这么久了吗？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">唔，可能还更久也说不定。总之，它似乎在这附近筑了巢，不肯走了。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">唉。第一年到这里的时候，我们可是能打上来不少好鱼呢！</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">……那时候，您在周围发现过其他的岛屿吗？</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">唔，那倒是没有。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">这附近瞭望不到别的陆地——没有充足的准备，就算是哥伦布也不敢轻率启航的。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">……是指淡水和干粮吗？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">唔，那些当然也是必不可少的——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——但关键在于，你需要一艘“强壮”的船。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesShoutClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">龙骨！三角帆和四角帆！这些才是最重要的。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">靠面前这条独木舟一样的家伙？没门。这里可不是风平浪静的太平洋。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">……</speak>
            <show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">不过，如果我们能干掉“利维坦”，那肯定有足够的人手愿意听我们的调遣，去建造大船。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">真的假的？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">哈哈。人类呐，不就是一种凭借信心来生存的物种吗？</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">举例来说，西班牙的士兵，面对着那些野蛮人，为什么常常能以少胜多？</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">不是我们真的强大到无法战胜——而是我们让敌人感受不到获胜的希望。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">若不然，仅凭一两百号冒险者，怎么能征服人口有数百万之多的秘鲁？</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">勒班陀海战以少胜多，那也是因为大家从气势上将敌人踩在了脚下——而不是靠什么临阵磨枪的威尼斯战船。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">您……来自帝国时期的西班牙吗？</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">噢，小姐好眼光啊。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">这可不是吹牛——在误打误撞闯进这个异世界之前，我可不光是退伍战士，还是个出了好几本书的文化人咧！</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">哼，听你这口气，多半也就是些卖不出去的孤芳自赏之作吧？</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">唔……我的确不知道它们在你们那个四百年后的时代还流行不流行了。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">《伽拉泰亚》，《贝尔西雷斯和西希斯蒙达》——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——以及，《堂·吉诃德·德·拉曼恰》。</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">您……</speak>
            <speak chara="_Rita" remark="next">您是……塞万提斯？</speak>
            <remark post="U2FsdGVkX19Bo9kqC3iZolEItRdA">
                <p class="article-text-h">Note：</p>
                <p class="article-text">米格尔·德·塞万提斯·萨维德拉（Miguel de Cervantes Saavedra, 1547 ~ 1616）是西班牙文学世界里最伟大的作家，甚至连西班牙语都被称为“塞万提斯的语言”。他的《堂吉诃德》，被认为是文学史上的第一部“现代小说”。</p>
                <p class="article-text">塞万提斯曾作为普通军人参加了1571年10月7日的勒班陀战役。在八年后撰写的一项官方报告中这样写道：“……在这场海战中，塞万提斯发着高烧，状态很差，连长和战友告诉他：你的情况很糟糕，应该好好躺在帆船的房间里。塞万提斯指责道：你们说什么呢，我没有尽到我应尽的义务，与其当怕死鬼，倒宁愿为了上帝和国王而战死……他就这样与战友们一起，像连长所命令的那样，在这场战斗中和土耳其人搏斗着。战斗结束后，胡安将军知晓了他的英勇表现，给了他额外的四个金币……在这场战役中，他的胸部和手部两处受伤，他的左手从此残废了。”</p>
            </remark>
            <goto goto="60" clockwise="1"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="60" background="beachIslandNoName.jpg">
            <bgm src="peerGynt.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Cervantes">Well aren't I pretty famous!</speak>
            <speak chara="_Cervantes">A master of literature! Hahaha, has a nice ring to it, I love it!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSighClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">And here I thought you were a soldier used to the battlefield... Who could have guessed you could be this smug.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSighClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Cervantes">Hahahaha! How could I not be happy after hearing that! You should smile too, miss Bianka!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Cervantes">It'll make you more motivated once we're out in the sea!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Hmph. Your concern is unneeded. There hasn't been a single day I haven't given my everything since I've become a Valkyrie at the age of 10.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaProudClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">If you teach me how, I'm confident I can learn how to catch fish or steer a ship perfectly.</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SmileClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">My my. By the way...</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">...Cervantes-san, how should we divide our roles once we sail?</speak>
            <show chara="rita17SquintClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Cervantes">Haha, don't be so stiff, miss. You can call me 「Miguel」.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">That's easy.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">I'll be the captain. I'll steer the ship, and judge when we should advance and retreat. As for you two——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Miss Bianka's specialty was spears, right? The harpoons are all yours.</speak>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Miss Rita is a very attentive person, so keep an eye on the anchor rope to make sure it doesn't get tangled.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Anchor rope? What is it for?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">That will, of course, be used to bring the ship closer to the beast.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Can't kill it if we're too far away, right? Also, we need to pick up his body and bring it back to the island for everyone to see. </speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">...What are we supposed to do if the 「Leviathan」 were to attack us? This reed boat is a little...</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">I'll make use of the currents to not give him the chance to attack us. It's that simple!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Oh right, didn't you two show something to the people on the island? A 「gun」 capable of even destroying boulders—— What was it called again...</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">...The all-purpose firing weapon of the previous civilization, 「2nd Relic」. Not a hard name to remember.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Hahahaha! We old people aren't good with long names.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">But anyway, we have a weapon stronger than the cannons of the Invincible Armada——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——What we're riding on isn't an unreliable reed boat... but a merciless hunting warship!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Remember this——</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">「Leviathan」, sea creatures, they're all just mere beasts. The only difference is their size.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">——And brave hunters can't possibly be afraid of a prey they're willingly approaching themselves.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——Yeah, you get it!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Now! Let's kill him!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesLaughClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <!-- RENAME: Look closely, old man. This is how a Valkyrie from 「Destiny」 fights! -->
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Look closely, old man. This is how a Valkyrie from 「Schicksal」 fights!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">(....)</speak>
            <speak chara="_Rita">(How can he say it's a 「mere beast」 with such confidence?)</speak>
            <goto goto="70" clockwise="1"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="70" background="seaWaveIslandNoName.jpg">
            <bgm src="seaAndSky.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">尽管之前徒步丈量过小岛的周长，也曾在岩山上的制高点俯瞰观察；但直到身处一片汪洋之中，两位女武神才真正感受到了她们“登陆场”的渺小。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">芦苇船只不过驶出了一刻钟的光景，身后这座容纳了数十人的“避难所”，便已经退化为一块难以辨识的绿色礁石，仿佛抬一抬手就能将它从天边抹去。</p>
            </text>
            <text>正午的阳光洒在海面上，粼粼的反光刺得人有些睁不开眼睛。</text>
            <text>老人轻摇长橹，将一叶扁舟稳定在翻滚的波浪之间。</text>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Careful. He's coming.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">...I don't sense anything near us.</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Yeah, but it's almost time.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">...Time?</speak>
            <show chara="rita17NormalClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">After the 「Leviathan」 gets a whiff that someone is out in the sea, it takes him approximately 15 minutes to catch up to the ship.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="biankaSeriousClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">I see——</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">——So that's why you stopped the ship here!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaSneerClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">That's right. The reef 5 meters below the ship protects us from any attack from beneath.</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">After all, we're using ourselves as bait—— Being careless can be fatal.</speak>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">And the opportunity to strike will only show itself for an instant——</speak>
            <bgm src="noise.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="cervantesShoutClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">——Wait, what's that sound!?</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesShoutClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17AngryClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">The sound of machinery!?</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">Look! There's something black under the water...!</speak>
            <show chara="biankaShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="cervantesGazeClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Is that... blood?</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesShoutClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="_Miguel">Something is fighting the 「Leviathan」 under the sea!</speak>
            <show chara="cervantesShoutClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
            <show chara="rita17AngryClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="_Rita">——It's coming!</speak>
            <goto goto="80" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="80" background="CG1.jpg">
            <bgm src="noise.mp3" status="stop"></bgm>
            <sound src="se_spring.mp3"/>
            <cg src="CG1.jpg" bg="CG1.jpg" fadeIn="0" fadeOut="1"></cg>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">That's...</speak>
            <speak chara="_Bianka">...A submarine!?</speak>
            <end post="U2FsdGVkX19d+mMVBhzEm6N2HRMF"/>
